WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.752 --> 00:00:03.378
ASTA: <i>Previously
on Resident Alien.</i>

2
00:00:03.462 --> 00:00:04.630
(ALL SCREAMING)

3
00:00:04.713 --> 00:00:06.757
ASTA: <i>So what happened to
the real Harry Vanderspeigle?</i>

4
00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:07.883
I don't know.

5
00:00:07.966 --> 00:00:09.551
BEN: Dr. Vanderspeigle.
the new doctor has arrived.

6
00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:11.803
Please call me Dr. Ethan.

7
00:00:11.887 --> 00:00:13.096
ALIEN HARRY:
I'm glad you know about me.

8
00:00:13.305 --> 00:00:15.057
ASTA: Nobody wants to hide
who they really are.

9
00:00:15.140 --> 00:00:17.976
You should stop feeling
guilty about giving away Jay.

10
00:00:18.060 --> 00:00:19.811
<i>She is a survivor.</i>

11
00:00:21.146 --> 00:00:23.106
(MOANS)
ASTA: He <i>will die.</i>

12
00:00:23.190 --> 00:00:25.734
My leg. chop it off.
(GRUNTS)

13
00:00:25.817 --> 00:00:28.487
<i>if Asta wasn't there.
I would be dead.</i>

14
00:00:28.570 --> 00:00:32.324
They took your spaceship. didn't
they? That means they're after you.

15
00:00:32.407 --> 00:00:36.036
It's probably MIB.
Men in Black.

16
00:00:36.119 --> 00:00:37.704
KATE: <i>I invited a friend
over with her husband.</i>

17
00:00:37.788 --> 00:00:39.498
This is Sarah
and Richard Houston.

18
00:00:39.581 --> 00:00:41.291
<i>You can babysit Max
whenever you want.</i>

19
00:00:41.375 --> 00:00:42.918
<i>LISA: Oh. I would love that.</i>

20
00:00:43.168 --> 00:00:45.170
DAVID: <i>You shouldn't have
taken that.</i> (COMPUTER DINGS)

21
00:00:45.462 --> 00:00:47.047
<i>Now the kid's gonna know
we were in his room.</i>

22
00:00:47.130 --> 00:00:50.008
Good. Then when he goes to
warn it. we'll be right on its tail.

23
00:00:50.092 --> 00:00:52.636
Asta! Are you in there?

24
00:00:54.221 --> 00:00:55.472
(SCREAMS)

25
00:00:55.556 --> 00:00:56.640
(BLUEGRASS MUSIC PLAYING)

26
00:00:56.807 --> 00:00:58.517
<i>If you kiss her.
you'll know it</i>

27
00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:00.435
<i>You'll never forget</i>

28
00:01:00.519 --> 00:01:03.021
<i>She's a little
French sweetheart...</i>

29
00:01:03.605 --> 00:01:05.857
ALIEN HARRY:
<i>Everyone has to die.</i>

30
00:01:05.941 --> 00:01:10.487
<i>It is the normal cycle of life for
beings across the entire universe.</i>

31
00:01:10.571 --> 00:01:12.447
<i>Some may live longer
than others.</i>

32
00:01:12.531 --> 00:01:17.077
<i>but every organism comes
into being and then ceases being.</i>

33
00:01:17.619 --> 00:01:19.162
(MUSIC STOPS)

34
00:01:23.375 --> 00:01:25.419
<i>The animals know this.</i>

35
00:01:25.502 --> 00:01:29.381
<i>They live in harmony with the
Earth. as it was meant to be.</i>

36
00:01:29.464 --> 00:01:33.343
<i>Everyone I kill with my device
is going to die anyway.</i>

37
00:01:33.427 --> 00:01:36.638
<i>At least I'm killing them
for a good reason.</i>

38
00:01:38.473 --> 00:01:40.475
<i>It's different for humans.</i>

39
00:01:40.559 --> 00:01:43.103
<i>Humans kill because they know
they're small.</i>

40
00:01:43.186 --> 00:01:45.314
<i>insignificant. weak.</i>

41
00:01:45.397 --> 00:01:48.358
<i>And killing makes them
feel strong.</i>

42
00:01:48.734 --> 00:01:51.069
<i>even if it's just
for a moment.</i>

43
00:02:15.344 --> 00:02:16.887
(SIGHS)

44
00:02:18.263 --> 00:02:20.974
(VIALS CLINKING)

45
00:02:37.449 --> 00:02:40.243
<i>And when humans are smart.</i>

46
00:02:40.327 --> 00:02:43.413
<i>they may even get away
with murder.</i>

47
00:02:51.838 --> 00:02:54.633
(WIND HOWLING)

48
00:02:58.679 --> 00:03:02.808
<i>Of course. no being really
gets away with anything.</i>

49
00:03:03.141 --> 00:03:05.894
(RADIO GLITCHES ON AND OFF)

50
00:03:10.107 --> 00:03:12.693
<i>The universe knows
what you have done.</i>

51
00:03:12.776 --> 00:03:15.362
<i>even if nobody else does.</i>

52
00:03:15.779 --> 00:03:18.615
(WIND CONTINUES HOWLING)

53
00:03:18.699 --> 00:03:21.493
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC)

54
00:03:29.751 --> 00:03:33.714
<i>And the universe will restore
balance one way or another.</i>

55
00:03:36.800 --> 00:03:38.760
<i>Humans have a word for this.</i>

56
00:03:40.387 --> 00:03:42.389
<i>They call it "karma."</i>

57
00:03:45.892 --> 00:03:47.978
