You damn near
gave me a heart attack

65
00:04:09.708 --> 00:04:11.376
banging on my door like that
at the crack of dawn.

66
00:04:11.460 --> 00:04:13.879
Oh. I'm so sorry
that finding the dead body

67
00:04:13.962 --> 00:04:15.881
