read you your rights."

134
00:06:30.056 --> 00:06:31.933
What do I say?
Tell me what I say.

135
00:06:32.142 --> 00:06:33.476
Tell me what I say.

136
00:06:33.560 --> 00:06:34.728
MIKE: That's the problem.
(D'ARCY GRUNTS)

137
00:06:34.811 --> 00:06:37.147
MIKE: Ow. ow. ow.
ow. ow. ow. ow!

138
00:06:37.230 --> 00:06:39.608
Okay. all right. all right.
all right. all right.

139
