There. she's stealing it.

144
00:07:15.644 --> 00:07:16.728
I knew it.

145
00:07:16.811 --> 00:07:19.814
She's a woman in a purple
skirt. man in black.

146
00:07:21.024 --> 00:07:22.901
We have to warn Harry.

147
00:07:42.170 --> 00:07:44.214
