LISA: Great. you distracted
me. now we're losing the little shit.

199
00:09:57.055 --> 00:09:59.432
Oh. my God.
Are you all right?

200
00:10:00.558 --> 00:10:03.019
Watch your
language. please.

201
00:10:03.728 --> 00:10:06.231
And you owe me $100
for the bike.

202
00:10:06.898 --> 00:10:08.024
Um...

203
00:10:08.108 --> 00:10:09.150
Looks fine to me.

204
00:10:09.526 --> 00:10:11.945
I'd be happy
to wait for the police.

205
00:10:12.529 --> 00:10:14.614
Pay the girl. You're the one
who made me run her over.

206
00:10:15.532 --> 00:10:16.741
Let's go.

207
00:10:16.950 --> 00:10:18.159
Now we've lost him.

208
00:10:20.411 --> 00:10:22.163
Pleasure.
(RV DOOR CLOSES)

209
00:10:23.039 --> 00:10:25.583
LISA: Taking so long.
DAVID: It's $100.

210
00:10:26.126 --> 00:10:28.962
(JAZZ MUSIC PLAYING
OVER RADIO)

211
00:10:29.420 --> 00:10:31.589
ALIEN HARRY: <i>My device
is at full power.</i>

212
00:10:31.673 --> 00:10:34.342
<i>With one press of the button.
the timer will begin.</i>

213
00:10:34.425 --> 00:10:36.427
<i>and roughly
90 Earth minutes later.</i>

214
00:10:36.511 --> 00:10:39.514
<i>8 billion humans
will cease to exist.</i>

215
00:10:39.597 --> 00:10:41.599
<i>This is the moment
I fulfill the mission</i>

216
00:10:41.683 --> 00:10:44.269
<i>that will change the course
of the universe forever.</i>

217
00:10:44.352 --> 00:10:46.229
<i>MAN ON</i> RADIO: <i>Are you dreaming of pizza?</i>

218
00:10:46.312 --> 00:10:47.939
<i>Mama Sap's Pizza is now open</i>

219
00:10:48.022 --> 00:10:49.774
<i>in the heart
of downtown Patience.</i>

220
00:10:50.567 --> 00:10:51.818
(GROANS)

221
00:10:57.115 --> 00:11:00.493
ALIEN HARRY: <i>[can't kill everyone
