222
00:11:00.577 --> 00:11:02.871
<i>(OUR TOWN</i> PLAYING)

223
00:11:02.954 --> 00:11:06.416
<i>And you know
The sun's setting fast</i>

224
00:11:06.499 --> 00:11:10.837
