What are you doing?
Nope.

750
00:37:43.470 --> 00:37:45.388
You got it for me.

751
00:37:45.472 --> 00:37:48.600
And you agree
with my doorknob instincts.

752
00:37:48.683 --> 00:37:50.685
You got decent
doorknob instincts. all right?

753
00:37:50.935 --> 00:37:51.978
But this whole thing
is for everybody.

754
00:37:52.061 --> 00:37:53.104
It ain't just for you.
Nope.

755
00:37:53.188 --> 00:37:54.230
What are you doing?
Nope.

756
00:37:54.355 --> 00:37:55.565
You got it for me.

757
00:38:07.118 --> 00:38:08.620
(TIRES SCREECHING)

758
00:38:10.830 --> 00:38:11.915
(INDISTINCT SHOUTING)

759
00:38:12.415 --> 00:38:13.875
(BRAKES SCREECHING)

760
00:38:14.125 --> 00:38:16.252
(ALARMS BLARING)

761
00:38:16.586 --> 00:38:17.796
You in the vehicle.

762
00:38:18.963 --> 00:38:20.465
Let me see your hands.

763
00:38:21.216 --> 00:38:23.760
(DEVICE SPEAKING
IN ALIEN LANGUAGE)

764
00:38:25.345 --> 00:38:26.596
(LOUD WHOOSH)

765
00:38:26.679 --> 00:38:28.097
(MEN GRUNTING)

766
00:38:37.440 --> 00:38:38.775
ALIEN HARRY: <i>I have
no choice now.</i>

767
00:38:38.858 --> 00:38:41.069
<i>since my device
will destroy me.</i>

768
00:38:41.736 --> 00:38:44.280
<i>I will fly away from here
and drop the device</i>

769
00:38:44.364 --> 00:38:47.784
<i>onto this beautiful planet
to finish the job I started.</i>

770
00:38:47.992 --> 00:38:50.787
(DISTANT HELICOPTER
BLADES WHIRRING)

771
00:39:00.672 --> 00:39:03.299
(LOUD BUZZING)

772
00:39:18.398 --> 00:39:19.482
Whoa.

773
00:39:27.073 --> 00:39:29.117
(VEHICLES APPROACHING)

774
00:39:31.786 --> 00:39:33.288
MAN: Go. go. go!

775
00:39:33.371 --> 00:39:35.874
(MEN SHOUTING)

776
00:39:36.165 --> 00:39:38.585
(DEVICE SPEAKING
IN ALIEN LANGUAGE)

777
00:39:39.419 --> 00:39:40.712
MAN: Double up. double up!

778
00:39:42.297 --> 00:39:43.548
Harry!

779
00:39:43.798 --> 00:39:45.633
(MEN SHOUTING)

780
00:39:46.467 --> 00:39:48.511
(SHIP WHIRRING)

781
00:39:48.595 --> 00:39:50.054
There's more!

782
00:39:50.972 --> 00:39:53.224
Freeze!
Hold it right there.

783
00:39:59.230 --> 00:40:00.732
Oh. no.

784
00:40:02.025 --> 00:40:03.735
I forgot the pizzas.

785
00:40:05.862 --> 00:40:08.907
(TIRES SQUEALING)

786
00:40:08.990 --> 00:40:11.117
ALIEN HARRY: <i>Maybe I can
go back and get them.</i>

787
00:40:11.200 --> 00:40:14.162
<i>I could take the ship and pick
them up on my way to space.</i>

788
00:40:16.789 --> 00:40:19.834
<i>I can't because
of this stupid mission.</i>

789
00:40:20.627 --> 00:40:22.045
(GRUNTING)

790
00:40:22.754 --> 00:40:24.547
<i>I am so hungry.</i>

791
00:40:25.757 --> 00:40:27.926
They look like black ants.

792
00:40:29.594 --> 00:40:31.846
(MEN GRUNTING)

793
00:40:35.266 --> 00:40:36.726
Where is your queen?

794
00:40:44.525 --> 00:40:45.777
MAN: Come on.

795
00:40:54.118 --> 00:40:56.037
(SIGHS)
Get down.

796
00:40:57.205 --> 00:40:58.665
Harry!

797
00:40:58.748 --> 00:41:00.416
(GROANS)

798
00:41:00.583 --> 00:41:03.419
(SHIP WHIRRING)

799
00:41:05.296 --> 00:41:08.424
<i>(O—O—H CHILD</i> PLAYING)

800
00:41:18.434 --> 00:41:20.478
<i>Ooh. child</i>

801
00:41:20.561 --> 00:41:24.023
<i>Things are gonna
Get easier</i>

802
00:41:24.107 --> 00:41:27.527
<i>Ooh. child
Things will get brighter</i>

803
00:41:29.737 --> 00:41:32.156
<i>Ooh. child...</i>

804
00:41:32.240 --> 00:41:33.574
Run. Max! Hide!

805
00:41:35.368 --> 00:41:38.746
<i>Ooh. child
Things will get brighter</i>

806
00:41:43.084 --> 00:41:44.335
Harry...

807
00:41:44.585 --> 00:41:46.462
I know why you're here.

808
00:41:46.546 --> 00:41:48.423
Don't do it.
Please don't do it.

809
00:41:48.506 --> 00:41:49.757
I must.

810
00:41:49.841 --> 00:41:52.844
It's why I came here.
I don't care.

811
00:41:53.094 --> 00:41:54.721
You're not the same.

812
00:41:54.887 --> 00:41:57.265
You've changed
since you came here.

813
00:41:57.348 --> 00:41:59.684
since you killed that man.
I've seen it.

814
00:42:00.101 --> 00:42:01.477
I just saw it now.

815
00:42:01.561 --> 00:42:04.063
You could've left.
but you stayed to help us.

816
00:42:04.230 --> 00:42:06.482
You've changed.
No.

817
00:42:06.733 --> 00:42:09.736
My mission is
to kill everyone.

818
00:42:12.030 --> 00:42:15.283
If you kill everyone.
you kill me.

819
00:42:20.747 --> 00:42:23.624
You are right.
I have changed. but...

820
00:42:24.125 --> 00:42:25.960
There's my friend.

821
00:42:27.211 --> 00:42:29.088
We are friends?

822
00:42:29.839 --> 00:42:31.299
Yes.

823
00:42:31.382 --> 00:42:33.134
We are friends.

824
00:42:35.762 --> 00:42:39.807
So. that means you will come
with me to my planet

825
00:42:39.891 --> 00:42:43.144
and we will kill everyone
on Earth together.

826
00:42:43.394 --> 00:42:45.354
What? No.

827
00:42:46.481 --> 00:42:48.441
I'm staying here.

828
00:42:53.446 --> 00:42:56.074
Then I won't kill everyone.

829
00:42:56.908 --> 00:42:58.659
(SIGHS)

830
00:42:58.743 --> 00:43:00.286
Okay. good.

831
00:43:03.039 --> 00:43:05.083
I will miss you. friend.

832
00:43:06.084 --> 00:43:07.418
I'll miss you. too. friend.

833
00:43:07.960 --> 00:43:09.462
(DEVICE SPEAKS IN
ALIEN LANGUAGE)

834
00:43:09.545 --> 00:43:11.339
I should dispose
of my device.

835
00:43:11.839 --> 00:43:14.467
It will kill everyone on Earth

836
00:43:14.550 --> 00:43:17.887
when it detonates
in 80 seconds.

837
00:43:18.096 --> 00:43:20.181
Oh. my God. Yes. Go.

838
00:43:21.349 --> 00:43:23.017
Go!

839
00:43:24.268 --> 00:43:26.104
(SIGHS)

840
00:43:26.562 --> 00:43:28.064
ALIEN HARRY: Real quick...

841
00:43:28.981 --> 00:43:31.526
I left some pizzas

842
00:43:31.609 --> 00:43:33.528
in my freezer.

843
00:43:34.487 --> 00:43:36.364
You can have them
if you want them.

844
00:43:37.031 --> 00:43:38.491
Thank you.

845
00:43:38.616 --> 00:43:40.076
Go!

846
00:43:41.452 --> 00:43:43.412
(SIGHS)

847
00:43:59.137 --> 00:44:01.973
(SHIP WHIRRING)

848
00:44:12.483 --> 00:44:15.403
ALIEN HARRY: <i>Everyone
has to die eventually.</i>

849
00:44:15.486 --> 00:44:19.407
<i>What matters are the choices
you make while you're alive.</i>

850
00:44:19.949 --> 00:44:22.952
<i>Killing may make humans
feel strong in the moment.</i>

851
00:44:23.035 --> 00:44:25.288
<i>but what We begun
to realize is.</i>

852
00:44:25.371 --> 00:44:28.791
<i>true strength comes
from choosing not to kill.</i>

853
00:44:28.958 --> 00:44:33.212
<i>Maybe being truly human is
about choosing to love instead.</i>

854
00:44:36.841 --> 00:44:40.803
<i>But with that love comes
the pain that I feel inside me.</i>

855
00:44:40.887 --> 00:44:42.847
<i>I need to go home.</i>

856
00:44:42.930 --> 00:44:46.726
<i>Hopefully the further I get
from them. the less I will care.</i>

857
00:44:46.976 --> 00:44:49.937
<i>Finally. I will be
at peace again.</i>

858
00:44:53.232 --> 00:44:57.403
(NERVOUSLY) Hi.
You're taking me home. right?

859
00:44:57.612 --> 00:44:59.697
This is some bullshit!

860
00:45:00.281 --> 00:45:01.324
Ugh.
